<article class="text">
	<header>
		<h1>Paginação</h1>
		<h3>Exibição de navegação por páginas.</h3>
	</header>
	<p>Navegação entre páginas.</p>

	<div class="example txt-center">
		<ul class="pagination">
			<li><a href="#">&laquo;</a></li>
			<li><a href="#">1</a></li>
			<li><a href="#">2</a></li>
			<li><a href="#">3</a></li>
			<li><a href="#">4</a></li>
			<li><a href="#">5</a></li>
			<li><a href="#">&raquo;</a></li>
		</ul>
	</div>

<pre class="lang-html prettyprint linenums">
&lt;ul class=&quot;pagination&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;&laquo;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;4&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;5&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;&raquo;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</pre>

	<h4>Estados Ativado e Desativado</h4>
	<p>Customize os links em diferentes circunstâncias. Utiliza a classe <code>.disabled</code> para links desativados e <code>.active</code> para indicar uma próxima pagina.</p>
	<div class="example txt-center">
		<ul class="pagination">
			<li class="disabled"><a href="#">&laquo;</a></li>
			<li class="active"><a href="#">1 </a></li>
			<li><a href="#">2</a></li>
			<li><a href="#">3</a></li>
			<li><a href="#">4</a></li>
			<li><a href="#">5</a></li>
			<li><a href="#">&raquo;</a></li>
		</ul>
	</div>

<pre class="lang-html prettyprint linenums">
&lt;ul class=&quot;pagination&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li class=&quot;disabled&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;&laquo;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li class=&quot;active&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;1 &lt;span class=&quot;sr-only&quot;&gt;(current)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	...
&lt;/ul&gt;
</pre>
	<p>Opcionalmente você também pode remover o link e manter apenas o <code>&lt;span&gt;</code> para manter o estilo e remover apenas a funcionalidade do click.</p>

<pre class="lang-html prettyprint linenums">
&lt;ul class=&quot;pagination&quot;&gt;
  &lt;li class=&quot;disabled&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;laquo;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li class=&quot;active&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;1 &lt;span class=&quot;sr-only&quot;&gt;(current)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  ...
&lt;/ul&gt;
</pre>

	<h4>Tamanhos</h4>
	<p>Para alterar o tamanho, utilize as classes <code>.pagination-lg</code> ou <code>pagination-sm</code></p>

	<div class="example txt-center">
		<div class="d-block">
			<ul class="pagination pagination-lg">
				<li><a href="#">&laquo;</a></li>
				<li><a href="#">1</a></li>
				<li><a href="#">2</a></li>
				<li><a href="#">3</a></li>
				<li><a href="#">4</a></li>
				<li><a href="#">5</a></li>
				<li><a href="#">&raquo;</a></li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div class="d-block">
			<ul class="pagination">
				<li><a href="#">&laquo;</a></li>
				<li><a href="#">1</a></li>
				<li><a href="#">2</a></li>
				<li><a href="#">3</a></li>
				<li><a href="#">4</a></li>
				<li><a href="#">5</a></li>
				<li><a href="#">&raquo;</a></li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div class="d-block">
			<ul class="pagination pagination-sm">
				<li><a href="#">&laquo;</a></li>
				<li><a href="#">1</a></li>
				<li><a href="#">2</a></li>
				<li><a href="#">3</a></li>
				<li><a href="#">4</a></li>
				<li><a href="#">5</a></li>
				<li><a href="#">&raquo;</a></li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>
<pre class="lang-html prettyprint linenums">
&lt;!-- Grande --&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;pagination pagination-lg&quot;&gt;...&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;!--	Normal --&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;pagination&quot;&gt;...&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;!--	Pequeno --&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;pagination pagination-sm&quot;&gt;...&lt;/ul&gt;
</pre>
	<h4>Paginador</h4>
	<p>Links rápidos para uma simples implementação de paginação com links de "anterior" e "próximo".</p>

	<div class="example">
		<ul class="pager">
			<li><a href="#">Previous</a></li>
			<li><a href="#">Next</a></li>
		</ul>
	</div>
<pre class="lang-html prettyprint linenums">
&lt;ul class=&quot;pager&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;Previous&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;Next&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</pre>

	<h4>links Alinhados</h4>
	<p>Você tem a opcão de alinhar um de cada lado</p>

	<div class="example">
		<ul class="pager">
			<li class="previous"><a href="#">&larr; Older</a></li>
			<li class="next"><a href="#">Newer &rarr;</a></li>
		</ul>
	</div>
<pre class="lang-html prettyprint linenums">
&lt;ul class=&quot;pager&quot;&gt;
  &lt;li class=&quot;previous&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;&amp;larr; Older&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li class=&quot;next&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;Newer &amp;rarr;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</pre>

	<h4>Estado desabilitado opcional</h4>
	<p>Esses links também usam a classe <code>.disabled</code> que é uma utilidade da paginação.</p>

	<div class="example">
		<ul class="pager">
			<li class="previous disabled"><a href="#">&larr; Older</a></li>
			<li class="next"><a href="#">Newer &rarr;</a></li>
		</ul>
	</div>
<pre class="lang-html prettyprint linenums">
&lt;ul class=&quot;pager&quot;&gt;
  &lt;li class=&quot;previous disabled&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;&amp;larr; Older&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li class=&quot;next&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;Newer &amp;rarr;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</pre>

